          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Encouraging Veteran Employment Act of 2018</b></p> <p>This bill authorizes the Department of Defense (DOD) to give preferential selection for DOD contracts to businesses that employ veterans based on the percentage of full-time employees who are veterans. </p> <p>A business that intentionally misrepresents the veteran status of its employees in a bid may be suspended or debarred from contract competition for at least five years.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2018-03-06T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
      </billSummaries>
